---
title: Italian Wedding-Style Beef and Pork Soup with Parmesan and Garlic Ciabatta
description: Cozy up with this homemade take on a classic Italian Wedding soup! Instead of forming time-consuming mini-meatballs, you'll break the beef and pork mixture into bite-sized pieces for a quicker alternative that doesn't sacrifice flavour.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/soupe-de-porc-et-de-boeuf-style-mariage-a-litalienne-0bcf0452.jpg
